<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Fixed exchange-rate system</h1>			<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
				<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>				<div id="contentSub"><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">  (Redirected from <a href="/w/index.php?title=Forex_fixing&amp;redirect=no" class="mw-redirect" title="Forex fixing">Forex fixing</a>)</span></div>
								<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
