<li id="cite_note-GS-26"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-GS_26-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-GS_26-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-GS_26-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation book">Garber, Peter M.; Svensson, Lars E. O. (1995). "The Operation and Collapse of Fixed Exchange Rate Regimes". <i>Handbook of International Economics</i>. <b>3</b>. Elsevier. pp.&#160;1865–1911. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.1016%2FS1573-4404%2805%2980016-4">10.1016/S1573-4404(05)80016-4</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=The+Operation+and+Collapse+of+Fixed+Exchange+Rate+Regimes&amp;rft.btitle=Handbook+of+International+Economics&amp;rft.pages=1865-1911&amp;rft.pub=Elsevier&amp;rft.date=1995&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1016%2FS1573-4404%2805%2980016-4&amp;rft.aulast=Garber&amp;rft.aufirst=Peter+M.&amp;rft.au=Svensson%2C+Lars+E.+O.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFixed+exchange-rate+system" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-suranovic-27"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-suranovic_27-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation book">Suranovic, Steven (2008-02-14). <i>International Finance Theory and Policy</i>. Palgrave Macmillan. p.&#160;504.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=International+Finance+Theory+and+Policy&amp;rft.pages=504&amp;rft.pub=Palgrave+Macmillan&amp;rft.date=2008-02-14&amp;rft.aulast=Suranovic&amp;rft.aufirst=Steven&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFixed+exchange-rate+system" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
</ol>
</div>
<p>(11) Feenstra, Robert C., and Alan M. Taylor. International Macroeconomics. New York: Worth, 2012. Print.</p>
